(327576, 10497, 325769, 'jog3ee', 4022, '', 1355577591, 'As I said, Hatsan 125 sniper is [B]the most powerful[/B] spring powered air-rifle in Pakistan which actually produces 950+fps with 14.3 grain pellets.. Its performance has been elaborated in various threads on this forum, you can go through them for details. The one that I have is fairly accurate and if I don''t mess up, it mostly hits where I aim. \n\nI have zero experience with the 350 magnum so I can''t comment on how it behaves. Its power ranges between 21-23 fpe.', 1, 0, '63.141.198.255', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
